ENG :
Map created by Mierzej. WARNING : The map is in BETA, so there may be different kinds of errors
This is a map "aim" for the fun to the game! 
P_90 weapon allows you to have fun in small map :).

Installing maps :
1. Unrar the file "aim_p90_v8"
2. Copy the files to your maps folder, which is located by default in:
(STEAM)
x:\Program files\Steam\Steamapps\(nickname)\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps
(NO-STEAM)
x:\Program files\counter-strike Source\cstrike\maps
